| `.opencode/lib/session-export.ts` | Shared export logic (types, constants, functions) |
| `.opencode/tools/export-session.ts` | Thin wrapper using lib |
| `.opencode/tools/git-commit.ts` | Uses lib for session export |

This eliminates duplication and keeps filtering logic in one place.

